<body>
<h1>The Colosseum, Rome</h1>
<center><img src="colossem.jpeg" style="width:350px; height:200px;"></center>
<p>
  The Colosseum is an oval amphitheatre in the centre of Rome, Italy. 
  It is the largest ancient amphitheatre ever built and remains the largest standing one in the world today.
</p>
